OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will continue to move
OL,7,Fsoutheastwards through this evening
OL,8,Fand overnight, turning heavy in
OL,9,Fplaces. Tending to become drier by
OL,10,Fdawn with some clearer spells
OL,11,Fdeveloping. Another muggy night to
OL,12,Fcome.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,15,Fspots of rain, especially over the
OL,16,Fhills. The cloud will break up
OL,17,Fthroughout the morning, leading to a
OL,18,Fmuch brighter afternoon. Feeling a tad
OL,19,Ffresher.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
