OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure building bringing plenty of
OL,7,Fdry and sunny weather. Temperatures
OL,8,Fincreasing by day and night with hot
OL,9,Fand humid conditions developing which
OL,10,Fmay trigger a few showers.
